pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef:<br />\n恒生（00011）表示，該行屯門鄉事會路分行一名員工經測試後初步確診新型肺炎，現正等待進一步檢測。該分行將由7月20日起暫時停止服務14天，以徹底清潔和消毒，而分行全部員工會留在家中自我隔離14天。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">總結：星展銀行我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">大家一齊Be strong, Be positive! </span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:35:40.000Z","msg":"又咩都推上連登<br />\n自己唔撚罷工咩<br />\n抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd880a01380f0a46d32e2c61c919ea7931dd705","tid":2121720,"uid":9521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:36:39.000Z","msg":"wfh玩ab team<br />\n但一定有人無份wfh咁解"},{"pid":"e1ab9e6d9be553189cdf749a619d4e10b8974b15","tid":2121720,"uid":189885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8f8e4d71a30c37ad1ffa897a9c493666af041cf","tid":2121720,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"43d26fbfe9353ba362da42882a307ae21a953377","tid":2121720,"uid":189885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"話說上星期六收到公司通知 有個清潔姐姐確診 <br />\n第二日先係公司官網出通知 極低調<br />\n正常一間銀行 仲要係尖沙咀 人流極高既情況下<br />\n都無任何媒體講過  你就知幾低調<br />\n<br />\n公司安排左員工做快速測試 消毒分行 （正常做法）<br />\n等結果期間 公司強調 個清潔姐姐係逗留少於30分鐘<br />\n而公司對於緊密接觸既定義 係「連續接觸30分鐘以上」<br />\n吹晒風向為之後唔隔離14日鋪路<br />\n<br />\n出左result之後 all negative<br />\n即刻叫班ops第二日返工 <br />\n班Sales 就繼續WFH 14日<br />\n仲要打<span class=\"red\">「我哋WFH 都必定全力配合分行服務！希望這段艱難嘅時候，可以順利度過。多謝大家！Be strong , Be positive!!」</span><br />\n<br />\n家下ops唔係人 sales就係人？？？？<br />\n根本就係推員工去死 <br />\n罔顧客戶安全<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef:<br />\n恒生（000